OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain and brisk winds will affect
OL,7,FScotland and Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fovernight. Patchy rain also moving in
OL,9,Facross west Wales and the far west of
OL,10,FEngland. Mainly dry with some clear
OL,11,Fintervals elsewhere. Warm, though more
OL,12,Fcomfortable than recently.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FRain affecting northern and
OL,15,Fwestern areas on Tuesday, turning
OL,16,Fincreasing showery. Some heavy,
OL,17,Fpossibly thundery outbreaks in the
OL,18,Fnorth. Patchy rain affecting southeast
OL,19,FEngland briefly, otherwise some warm
OL,20,Fsunshine here.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
